@rmarkello and @danjgale - what do you guys think about publishing this toolbox in a short paper?

I haven't done it but I thought of the "Research and Ideas" (RIO) paper or perhaps the F1000, as mentioned by Ariel or was it Cameron? I imagine something short as this: https://riojournal.com/article/12342/

We can also just package into a zenodo thingy, but I like RIO or F1000 more as it is also considered by google scholar.

